descript.abstract: Polygons representing area contained by Voting Precincts for Santa Barbara County. These precinct polygons have been aligned and registered to the Assessor's Parcel basemap (dated 6/28/2012) where boundaries are coincident.
descript.purpose: For general mapping, analysis and cartographic displays on precinct and vote center maps for the November 3, 2015 General Election. Cartographic displays generated from this spatial data are typically presented at a map scale less than 1:6000.
